fourth defeat of the season, Raymond displayed none of the zip she
had shown against the Swiss teenager as Tauziat broke her twice on
the way to winning the first set.
</P>
<P>
While Raymond was able to fight her way back from a similar one
set deficit against Hingis, there were no such heroics against
Tauziat who matched the American shot-for-shot in the second
before breaking her at 6-5 to win the match.  
