<TEXT>
<P>
LANZHOU, October 18 (Xinhua) -- Two 300,000-kw generating
units, part of the second phase of construction of the Jingyuan
Power Plant in northwest China's Gansu Province, went into
operation today, making the plant the largest in northwest China.
</P>
